Package: AdvRknapsack
Type: Package
Title: Solutions to Knapsack Problem Using Various Algorithms
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-10-14
Author: Nisal Amasha Rajapaksha and Uday Jain
Maintainer: Uday Jain <uday9k@gmail.com>
Description: Provides multiple algorithms for solving the knapsack problem, including Brute-Force, Greedy, 
    and Dynamic Programming approaches. The package includes functions to optimize the selection of items 
    based on weight and value constraints, with options for parallel execution and performance optimizations.
